<i>crydium] Colensoi, Hook. </i>A small tree 20-40 ft. high ..., very similar in mode of growth to <i>intermedium, ..</i>56] <i>ver-pine; Monoao</i>. The wood is yellowish-white, ... very durable. [Discusses confusion with <i>Dacrydium</i> (Hooker's Podocarpus?) <i>biforme</i>, although two species different]
